com.ge.research.sadl.server

Interface ISadlServerMD

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ISadlServer, ISadlServerPE
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SadlServerMDImpl

    public interface ISadlServerMD
extends ISadlServerPE
    This Interface class defines additional methods beyond those in the super classes SadlServer and SadlServerPE. These methods are primarily convenience functions to support model-driven application, e.g., model-driven user-interface. MD--model-driven => SadlServerMD
    Author:
    Andy Crapo
